Output tapes/screenshots/test-layout.png

Set Shell "zsh"
Set Width 1200
Set Height 800
Set FontSize 14
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Type "DOPS_NO_ALT_SCREEN=1 ./dops"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Screenshot tapes/screenshots/layout-initial.png

Down
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 2s

Screenshot tapes/screenshots/layout-run.png

Type "q"
Sleep 500ms
